WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.160
I was just there to serve drinks, that's it.

2
00:00:02.160 --> 00:00:05.519
So Heather, how much do you charge for a night of waitressing?

3
00:00:05.519 --> 00:00:08.560
An escort by Nye, and a doormat by day.

4
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:12.400
No, that's not- I would never.

5
00:00:12.400 --> 00:00:14.320
Oh, spare us the innocent act?

6
00:00:16.399 --> 00:00:18.800
The new head of marketing will be at the party tonight.

7
00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:20.079
So why don't you put your...

8
00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:21.440
talents?

9
00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:22.960
Good use.

10
00:00:24.989 --> 00:00:25.789
No.

11
00:00:25.789 --> 00:00:26.910
Absolutely not.

12
00:00:26.910 --> 00:00:27.870
I won't do it.

13
00:00:27.870 --> 00:00:28.989
Oh, but you will.

14
00:00:29.710 --> 00:00:32.189
Unless you want the entire company to find out about

15
00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:34.380
your junky brother?

16
00:00:36.689 --> 00:00:38.450
Play nice with the new boss.

